data.description: Popular single level Manzanita floor plan featuring a spacious deck spanning the entire back and side of the property with a peek-a-boo view of the ocean.  Situated at the end of the cul-de-sac offering privacy and located behind the gates of the San Luis Bay Estates in the Pelican Point community.  Open concept featuring ~1548 sq ft with 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, vaulted ceilings, a cozy fireplace and hardwood floors extending to the dining area, kitchen and office/ 3rd bedroom. With access to the expansive deck from the living room, dining area and primary suite, you'll  enjoy the ease of access from indoor to outdoor entertaining and the ideal place to relax amid the peaceful sounds and sights of nature. Ample storage available in the 2 car attached garage plus a separate golf cart garage. Experience hiking and biking trails that lead to the beach, the Bob Jones Trail, the Avila Bay Athletic Club and the Avila Golf course. Exceptional opportunity for a vacation home, 2nd home or why not live the Avila Beach resort lifestyle every day?
